	(text "7.3.2 Setting LED Current:\n\nR_{SNS} = V_{FB_REF} / I_{LED}\n\nV_{FB_REF} is fixed at 0.099 V, I_{LED} = 0.700 A\n\n0.099 / 0.700 = 141 mΩ (next common size = 143 mΩ)"
